[25/10/2018 14:20:39] <font color="#ffffff">-A ver, a ver.</font>
[25/10/2018 14:20:39] <font color="#ffffff">-Decía...</font>
[25/10/2018 14:20:41] <font color="#ffffff">Ah, sí, eh...</font>
